snippet.title: Tales of Frah'Akin Trailer
snippet.description:
Hello! 
The first official trailer for Tales of Frah'Akin is here! I'm very excited to show you a glimpse of what's to come. Stay tuned for an upcoming devlog!

✨Try the demo:
🔗 Steam: https://bit.ly/46S7fBg
🔗 Itch: https://bit.ly/3YQe7wQ

✨Follow the upcoming Kickstarter Campaign:
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/tales-of-frahakin/tales-of-frahakin

✨Watch my introduction to Tales of Frah'Akin:
https://youtu.be/v7Zs1uO9vKk
